leadingComments.value: This software comes with ABSOLUTELY NO WARRANTY. For details, see
the enclosed file COPYING for license information (GPL). If you
did not receive this file, see https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt.

*
 * Process supplied query params and return a query string.
 *
 * @param {Object} query Object containing query parameters as key/value pairs. Supported value types are:
 *   - array (will append duplicate parameter names with separate values)
 *   - object (will be converted to JSON)
 *   - boolean (will be converted to 0/1)
 *   - string
 *   - number
 * @returns {String} Complete query string with URI encoded values and prepended with a question mark (?).
